<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ジュード</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Jude</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milla</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>世界樹が壊されたりしたら
この世界はもっと酷い事になってしまう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If the World Tree were destroyed,
things would be even worse for this world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕はもう、誰にも死んでほしくないんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't want anyone else to die...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうか。
それが君の戦う理由なんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see. So that's what you fight for.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん。
ミラみたいに、胸を張って
使命だなんて到底言えないけどね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. I probably say with total conviction
that it's my mission like you can, though.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なぜだ？
君の戦う理由は、十分立派だと思うが？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why is that?
I find your reasons for fighting quite splendid.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あ、ありがとう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Th-Thanks.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>君は優しいんだな。
それが君の強さなのだろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're a kind person.
That is your strength, is it not?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だが……優しさは時に危険だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And yet... kindness can sometimes be dangerous.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
